<i>adverb</i>: 좌르르 [좌르르], 원활히 [원활히], 원만히 [원만히], 술술 [술술], 순탄히 [순ː탄히], 솔솔 [솔솔], 소르르 [소르르], 살살 [살살], 뽀송뽀송 [뽀송뽀송], 번드르르 [번드르르], 미끈미끈 [미끈미끈], 무난히 [무난히], 매끈히 [매끈히], 매끈매끈 [매끈매끈], 막힘없이 [마키멉씨], 달달 [달달], 나긋나긋 [나근나귿] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>좌르르 [좌르르]</dt><br>
<dd>1. quickly</dd><br>
<dd>물줄기 따위가 잇따라 세차게 쏟아지는 소리. 또는 그 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>With a sound resembling one that is produced when a flow of water, etc., keeps falling down forcefully, or such an action.</dd><br>
<dd>2. quickly</dd><br>
<dd>여러 개의 작은 물체가 잇따라 쏟아지는 소리. 또는 그 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>With a sound resembling one that is produced when many small objects keep falling down, or such an action.</dd><br>
<dd>3. smoothly; tastily</dd><br>
<dd>얼굴이나 밥 따위에 윤기가 흐르는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In such a manner that facial skin, steamed rice, etc., looks slick.</dd><br>
<dd>4. with a smooth motion</dd><br>
<dd>미닫이문이 미끄러지듯 가볍게 열리거나 닫히는 소리. 또는 그 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>With a sound resembling one that is produced when a sliding door opens or closes smoothly and softly, or such an action.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>원활히 [원활히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. smoothly</dd><br>
<dd>까다로운 데가 없이 원만하게.</dd><br>
<dd>Amicably without being fussy.</dd><br>
<dd>2. smoothly</dd><br>
<dd>막힘이 없이 순조롭고 매끄럽게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a smooth and peaceful manner without a hitch.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>원만히 [원만히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. mildly; gently</dd><br>
<dd>성격이 부드럽고 너그럽게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of one's personality being gentle and generous.</dd><br>
<dd>2. smoothly; peacefully</dd><br>
<dd>일의 진행이 순조롭게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a state in which the progress of something is smooth.</dd><br>
<dd>3. intimately; harmoniously</dd><br>
<dd>서로 사이가 좋게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of getting along well with each other.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>술술 [술술]</dt><br>
<dd>1. smoothly</dd><br>
<dd>물이나 가루 등이 틈이나 구멍으로 잇따라 조금씩 새어 나오는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing water, powder, etc., coming through a crack or hole little by little.</dd><br>
<dd>2. gently</dd><br>
<dd>바람이 부드럽게 부는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing the wind blowing softly.</dd><br>
<dd>3. lightly</dd><br>
<dd>가는 비나 눈이 잇따라 가볍게 내리는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing a fine rain or snow falling lightly.</dd><br>
<dd>4. fluently; smoothly</dd><br>
<dd>말이나 글이 막힘없이 잘 나오거나 써지는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of speaking or writing without hesitation.</dd><br>
<dd>5. smoothly</dd><br>
<dd>묶이거나 엉킨 실이나 끈이 쉽게 잘 풀리는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing a tangled or bound thread or string disentangling easily.</dd><br>
<dd>6. easily</dd><br>
<dd>해결하기 어려운 일이나 문제가 쉽게 풀리는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of a knotty or difficult problem being solved easily.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>순탄히 [순ː탄히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. (no equivalent expression)</dd><br>
<dd>성질이 까다롭지 않게.</dd><br>
<dd>In such a manner that the personality of someone is not fussy.</dd><br>
<dd>2. smoothly</dd><br>
<dd>길이 험하지 않고 평탄하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In such a manner that the road is not rough but smooth.</dd><br>
<dd>3. smoothly</dd><br>
<dd>삶이나 과정 등이 문제없이 순조로이.</dd><br>
<dd>In such a manner that the process of something, the life of someone, etc., is smooth without any problems.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>솔솔 [솔솔]</dt><br>
<dd>1. smoothly</dd><br>
<dd>물이나 가루 등이 틈이나 구멍으로 조금씩 새어 나오는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing water, powder, etc., coming through a crack or hole little by little.</dd><br>
<dd>2. gently</dd><br>
<dd>바람이 부드럽게 부는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing the wind blowing softly.</dd><br>
<dd>3. lightly</dd><br>
<dd>가는 비나 눈이 잇따라 가볍게 내리는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing a fine rain or snow falling lightly.</dd><br>
<dd>4. fluently; smoothly</dd><br>
<dd>말이나 글이 막힘없이 잘 나오거나 써지는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of speaking or writing without hesitation.</dd><br>
<dd>5. smoothly</dd><br>
<dd>묶이거나 엉킨 실이나 끈이 쉽게 잘 풀리는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing a tangled or bound thread or string disentangling easily.</dd><br>
<dd>6. easily</dd><br>
<dd>해결하기 어려운 일이나 문제가 쉽게 풀리는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of a knotty or difficult problem being solved easily.</dd><br>
<dd>7. lightly</dd><br>
<dd>가볍게 냄새가 나거나 연기가 피어오르는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of a smell or smoke rising lightly.</dd><br>
<dd>8. quietly</dd><br>
<dd>재미가 은근히 나는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of feeling interested quietly.</dd><br>
<dd>9. slowly; quietly</dd><br>
<dd>잠에 조금씩 빠지는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of falling asleep slowly.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>소르르 [소르르]</dt><br>
<dd>1. smoothly; readily</dd><br>
<dd>얽히거나 뭉친 물건이 쉽게 잘 풀리는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing a tangled thing unwinding easily.</dd><br>
<dd>2. gently</dd><br>
<dd>바람이 천천히 부드럽게 불어오는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing the wind blowing slowly and softly.</dd><br>
<dd>3. quietly</dd><br>
<dd>물이나 가루 등이 조용히 부드럽게 새어 나오는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing water, powder, etc., coming through something quietly and softly.</dd><br>
<dd>4. quietly</dd><br>
<dd>살며시 졸음이 오거나 잠이 드는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing one falling asleep or dozing off quietly.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>살살 [살살]</dt><br>
<dd>1. stealthily</dd><br>
<dd>남이 알아차리지 못하게 천천히 조용하게 행동하는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of acting slowly and quietly so that others do not know.</dd><br>
<dd>2. imperceptibly; softly</dd><br>
<dd>눈이나 설탕 등이 모르는 사이에 저절로 녹는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of snow, sugar, etc., melting away before one knows.</dd><br>
<dd>3. softly; gently</dd><br>
<dd>세지 않게 만지거나 문지르는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of touching or rubbing something tenderly.</dd><br>
<dd>4. adroitly; gently</dd><br>
<dd>겉으로 드러나지 않게 은근히 설득하는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of persuading someone indirectly so that one's intention is not revealed.</dd><br>
<dd>5. gently</dd><br>
<dd>바람이 가볍고 부드럽게 부는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing the wind blowing lightly and softly.</dd><br>
<dd>6. gently</dd><br>
<dd>가볍게 눈웃음을 치는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of smiling with one's eyes lightly.</dd><br>
<dd>7. smoothly</dd><br>
<dd>얽힌 실 등이 잘 풀리는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of tangled thread, etc., disentangling easily.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>뽀송뽀송 [뽀송뽀송]</dt><br>
<dd>1. in a dry and tender state</dd><br>
<dd>잘 말라서 물기가 없고 보드라운 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of being dried yet soft.</dd><br>
<dd>2. smoothly; softly</dd><br>
<dd>피부나 얼굴이 곱고 보드라운 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In a state in which one's skin or face is soft and smooth.</dd><br>
<dd>3. fuzzily; downily</dd><br>
<dd>매우 작고 보드라운 털 같은 것이 돋아 있는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of having very short, soft hair or something similar.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>번드르르 [번드르르]</dt><br>
<dd>glossily; smoothly</dd><br>
<dd>윤기가 있고 미끄러운 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of being glossy and smooth.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>미끈미끈 [미끈미끈]</dt><br>
<dd>smoothly; sleekly</dd><br>
<dd>울퉁불퉁하거나 거친 데가 없이 몹시 부드러운 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of being very soft without uneven or rough parts.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>무난히 [무난히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. easily; smoothly</dd><br>
<dd>어려움이나 장애가 별로 없이.</dd><br>
<dd>With few difficulties or obstacles.</dd><br>
<dd>2. without defects</dd><br>
<dd>두드러지는 단점이나 흠이 없이.</dd><br>
<dd>Without a recognizable shortcoming or defect.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>매끈히 [매끈히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. smoothly; sleekly</dd><br>
<dd>울퉁불퉁하거나 거친 데가 없이 미끄럽고 보드랍게.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing a very smooth look without any bumpy or rough spot.</dd><br>
<dd>2. cleanly; nicely</dd><br>
<dd>겉모습이 훤하고 말끔하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In an appearance that is clean and groomed.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>매끈매끈 [매끈매끈]</dt><br>
<dd>smoothly; sleekly</dd><br>
<dd>울퉁불퉁하거나 거친 데가 없이 아주 보드라운 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing a very smooth look without any bumpy or rough spot.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>막힘없이 [마키멉씨]</dt><br>
<dd>easily; smoothly</dd><br>
<dd>방해받는 것이 없이 쉽게.</dd><br>
<dd>Easily without any obstacles.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>달달 [달달]</dt><br>
<dd>1. quiveringly</dd><br>
<dd>춥거나 무서워서 몸을 계속해서 떠는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing the movement of one's body quivering continuously with cold or fear.</dd><br>
<dd>2. with a wobble</dd><br>
<dd>작은 바퀴가 단단한 바닥을 구르며 흔들리는 소리. 또는 그 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word imitating the sound or describing the movement of a small wheel rolling and wobbling on the hard ground.</dd><br>
<dd>3. smoothly; with fluency</dd><br>
<dd>막힘이 없이 시원시원하게 외는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of reciting fluently and without hesitation.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>나긋나긋 [나근나귿]</dt><br>
<dd>1. smoothly; softly</dd><br>
<dd>피부로 전해지는 느낌이 매우 연하고 부드러운 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of feeling soft and mild on the skin.</dd><br>
<dd>2. mildly; amiably</dd><br>
<dd>성격이나 태도가 매우 상냥하고 부드러운 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>With a very kind and soft personality or attitude.</dd><br>
